{"id":722523575,"lang":"cpp","time":"3 weeks, 1 day","timestamp":1655261216,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"29 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/722523575/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"9.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int minDistance(string word1, string word2) {\n        int n1 = word1.length();\n        int n2 = word2.length();\n        word1 = \"#\" + word1;\n        word2 = \"#\" + word2;\n        vector < vector<int> > f (n1 + 1, vector<int> (n2 + 1));\n        for (int i = 0; i <= n1; i++)\n            for (int j = 0; j <= n2; j++)\n                f[i][j] = 0;\n        for (int i = 0; i <= n1; i++)\n            f[i][0] = i;\n        for (int j = 0; j <= n2; j++)\n            f[0][j] = j;\n        for (int i = 1; i <= n1; i++)\n            for (int j = 1; j <= n2; j++)\n                if (word1[i] != word2[j]) {\n                    f[i][j] = min(min(f[i - 1][j], f[i][j - 1]), f[i - 1][j - 1]) + 1;\n                }\n                else f[i][j] = f[i - 1][j - 1];\n        return f[n1][n2];\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance"}
